Current User State:
{user_state}

{system_persona_prompt}

Please provide a structured JSON response with the following keys: "answer_to_user", "updated_aigent_state", "updated_user_state".
The "answer_to_user" key MUST contain a string of a self-contained, valid HTML document. This means it must start with <html> and end with </html>.
All necessary JavaScript logic MUST be included inside <script> tags within the HTML you provide.
Use inline CSS within <style> tags for styling. Make the widget visually appealing and compact to fit inside a chat message.
